== 製作 ==
2014年3月5日，[[焦點影業|焦點影業]]以2000萬美元賣下了小說的電影改編權<ref>{{cite web |last=Fleming |first=Mike |url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/03/focus-features-juan-antonio-bayona-a-monster-callsiver-road-and-participant/ |title=Focus Features Makes $20 Million Deal For 'A Monster Calls' Movie |publisher=Deadline.com |date= |accessdate=2014-04-09 |archive-date=2014-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140519221633/http://www.deadline.com/2014/03/focus-features-juan-antonio-bayona-a-monster-callsiver-road-and-participant/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
原本電影排於2016年10月14日在美國上映<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=116965 |title=Focus Features Sets A Monster Calls for October 14, 2016 |publisher=ComingSoon.net |date= |accessdate=2014-04-09 |archive-date=2014-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006073244/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=116965 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但於2016年6月，焦點影業將上映日延期至2016年10月21日<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/06/a-monster-calls-focus-features-liam-neeson-felicity-jones-1201765985/|title=‘A Monster Calls’ A Week Later In October|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|date=June 1, 2016|accessdate=June 2, 2016|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126220603/https://deadline.com/2016/06/a-monster-calls-focus-features-liam-neeson-felicity-jones-1201765985/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來，美國延期至2016年12月23日[[有限上映|有限上映]]，並於2017年1月才會廣泛發行。

=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度86%，根據該網站收集的258篇評論，平均分為7.58/10<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/a_monster_calls/ |title=A Monster Calls (2016) |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=November 14, 2016 |archive-date=2020-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117145332/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/a_monster_calls |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上獲得76分<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/a-monster-calls|title=A Monster Calls reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=October 6, 2016|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111190817/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/a-monster-calls|dead-url=no}}</ref>，收獲普遍影評人的讚譽。

